∀ {α : Type u} [inst : LinearOrderedField α] {a b c : α},
  ∀ {A B C : EuclideanGeometry.Triangle α}, EuclideanGeometry.rightTriangle A B C →
  EuclideanGeometry.sideLength A C = a →
  EuclideanGeometry.sideLength B C = b →
  EuclideanGeometry.sideLength A B = c →
  c ^ 2 = a ^ 2 + b ^ 2

∀ {α : Type u} [inst : EuclideanGeometry α] (A B C : α),
  RightTriangle A B C →
  let a := (B - C).length
  let b := (A - C).length
  let c := (A - B).length
  c ^ 2 = a ^ 2 + b ^ 2

∀ {α : Type u} [inst : EuclideanGeometry α] {A B C : α},
  RightTriangle A B C →
    (∃ (a b c : ℝ), a = dist B C ∧ b = dist A C ∧ c = dist A B ∧ c^2 = a^2 + b^2)

∀ {α : Type u} [inst : LinearOrderedField α] {a b c : α},
  ∀ (A B C : EuclideanGeometry.Point α), 
    EuclideanGeometry.Triangle.RightTriangle A B C →
      EuclideanGeometry.Triangle.Hypotenuse A B C = c →
        EuclideanGeometry.Triangle.Leg A C = a →
          EuclideanGeometry.Triangle.Leg B C = b →
            c^2 = a^2 + b^2

∀ {α : Type u} [inst : InnerProductSpace ℝ α] {A B C : α} (h : ∠ A C B = π / 2),
  let a := dist B C,
      b := dist A C,
      c := dist A B in
  c ^ 2 = a ^ 2 + b ^ 2
∀ {α : Type u} [inst : LinearOrderedField α] {a b c : α}, right_triangle a b c → c^2 = a^2 + b^2

∀ {α : Type u} [inst : EuclideanGeometry α] {A B C : α}, RightAngle A B C →
  ∀ (a b c : ℝ), a = Distance B C → b = Distance A C → c = Distance A B → a^2 + b^2 = c^2

∀ {α : Type u} [inst : LinearOrderedField α] {a b c : α},
  ∃ (A B C : α → α → Prop),
    A a b → B b c → C a c → a^2 + b^2 = c^2

∀ {α : Type} [EuclideanGeometry α] {A B C : α},
  RightTriangle A B C → ∀ (a b c : ℝ), a = dist B C → b = dist A C → c = dist A B → a^2 + b^2 = c^2
